-- U.K. Government Aims to Support Carbon Price in Energy Review, Huhne Says
-- Reed Landberg
-- 2010-07-27T11:41:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-27/u-k-government-aims-to-support-carbon-price-in-energy-review-huhne-says.html

          
          
             The U.K. government is conducting a
review of electricity market regulations, aiming to boost the
price of carbon and spur renewable power providers, Energy
Secretary Chris Huhne said in a statement to Parliament in
London today.  
          
          


  


        